As Tyrael was flying back to the Tripred ship, the falling artifact 
fell hard and fast on the shields. It rebounded some meters away, and 
it seemed to be burning hot. What could that thing be?

Tyrael: Cheetah, new orders. Meet me where this thing crashed, we 
shall investigate.

It was a good way to test the newcomer and to know his strength and 
weaknesses, Tyrael thought. He did wonder, however, what the object 
was and how it could have crashed directly on the base.
